race.comment: HURSTVILLE ZAGREB (2) consistent on-speed gelding who gave them a galloping lesson at his second run back with the 59.5kg when scoring over 1600m at Warwick Farm. Proven at this trip and expect to see him go quickly through his grades this time in. BRAVE CALL (5) imported gelding who comes down from Queensland for the Kris Lees yard third-up. Will relish the good tempo and shapes as a key contender with Berry aboard. ADOLPHUS (10) from the in-form Matt Dale yard and brings a solid set of figures to compete at this level. Was a month between runs when taking control early from the outside gate with a tenacious win over 1500m at this track in Highway class. Will run the trip right out at the good each way quote. LUSKAIRE (3) gone to a new level this prep and races best with his runs spaced. Can stalk the speed and play a leading role. BROSNAN (1) back in grade after surging late down the outside when third over this track and trip at latest. Key jockey change today. Respect.
